{#- ### Mitigations — per-component tables with a Priority column.
    Inputs:
      groups : list of { header, include_affects_column, mitigations[] }
              `mitigations[i]` carries
                { id, title, component_list[{id,name}], primary_component_id,
                  addresses[{ref,label}], effort, priority }
      intro  : top-of-section paragraph string

    Each `groups` entry renders as one H4 + one markdown table. The
    `include_affects_column` flag adds an "Affects" column in front of
    "Addresses" for groups that intentionally span multiple components
    (Cross-Component Mitigations + the > 10-component flat layout).
-#}
### Mitigations

